This repository contains thesis-related extensions and modifications by Madhuram Mantri.

This work builds upon the original repository:
multi_robot_navigation by David Dudas
https://github.com/dudasdavid/multi_robot_navigation

Original work is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Modifications in this repository include thesis-specific development related to:
- merged-map frontier exploration
- Voronoi-based coordination
- goal claiming
- TF-stability-gated stopping
- optional ORB-SLAM3 and EKF-based localization fusion

Parts of the code and documentation in this repository were developed with AI-assisted support.
All final integration, adaptation, validation, and thesis-specific implementation decisions were made by Madhuram Mantri.

